<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1080</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 xī biān yǒu tiáo fā guāng de lù ya, xī biān yǒu tiáo fā guāng de lù.
 fā guāng de lù shàng yǒu rén zài chuán jiǎng zhǔ yé sū.
 bó lì héng de dà mài huáng le, bó lì héng de dà mài huáng le.
 bō ā sī yǐ zhàn zài tián jiān. shōu gē de rén kuài lái.
 zhǔ de ēn diǎn dà yòu guǎng a, wǒ men zěn néng bù gē chàng!
 tā zhèng zài xíng xīn shì qí shì, hái yǒu wǒ men de gù xiāng.</lyrics>
<title>xī biān yǒu tiáo fā guāng de lù 迦南1080</title>
</song>